<section xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" version="5.0" id="MathTrig">
  <title>Trigonometric Functions</title>

  <para>
    Opcodes that perform trigonometric functions are:
    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem><para><link linkend="cos"><citetitle>cos</citetitle></link>, <link linkend="cosh"><citetitle>cosh</citetitle></link> and <link linkend="cosinv"><citetitle>cosinv</citetitle></link></para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem><para><link linkend="sin"><citetitle>sin</citetitle></link>, <link linkend="sinh"><citetitle>sinh</citetitle></link> and <link linkend="sininv"><citetitle>sininv</citetitle></link></para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem><para><link linkend="tan"><citetitle>tan</citetitle></link>, <link linkend="tanh"><citetitle>tanh</citetitle></link>, <link linkend="taninv"><citetitle>taninv</citetitle></link>, and <link linkend="taninv2"><citetitle>taninv2</citetitle></link>.</para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </para>

</section>
